<![CDATA[<div style="text-align: right;"><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;"><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000066" size="6">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></span></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" color="#ff6600" size="4"><i>Charter<font size="4">ed By&nbsp;</font>The British Schools&nbsp;<font size="4">Founda<font size="4">t<font size="4">ion</font></font></font><br></i></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" color="#c0c0c0" size="6"><b><i><br></i></b></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" color="#ff6600" size="1"><i><br></i></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" style=""><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.Salutation} {!Contact.LastName},</span></font></div><span lang="en-GB" style="text-align: start;"><div style="margin: 0px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><div class="gmail_quote" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div dir="ltr"><br><div>World Book Day is an annual international day to promote a love of reading. Traditionally it is celebrated on April 23rd to honour the death of William Shakespeare.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>In the UK, they celebrate it earlier - on the 1st Thursday in March - because the 23rd April usually falls during the Easter holidays.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>As the 23rd April will be the first day back from the Easter holidays, the secondary school will be celebrating World Book Day on Tuesday April 24th. Students and staff are encouraged to dress up as their favourite book character.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>We are writing to let you know this, so that you have plenty of time to discuss your child's costume with them. There will be prizes for the best costume. There will also be other reading themed events, which I will communicate closer to the time.</div><div><br></div><div>Kind regards,&nbsp;</div><span class="m_8480517120136221138HOEnZb"><div><br></div><div>Rebecca</div><span class="HOEnZb"><div><br></div><div><br></div><div><div class="m_8480517120136221138m_-2096060360399836893gmail_signature" data-smartmail="gmail_signature"><div dir="ltr">Rebecca Kearon-Wiles<div><br><div>English and Drama Teacher</div><div>7A Form Tutor</div></div></div></div></div></span></span></div><div class="yj6qo"></div><div class="adL"></div></div><font color="#000000" size="3"><br><br></font></font></div></span><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style=""><i style=""><font class="Apple-style-span" style="" face="Arial, sans-serif">World Class Education</font></i></span></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">__________________________________________________________</font></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">{!User.School_List_Email_Footer__c}</font></div></div>]]></td>
